```

### Interactivity Components

#### ChartTooltip

```jsx
<Chart data={data}>
  <Bar>
    <ChartTooltip>{(datum) => <div>Average: {datum.average}</div>}</ChartTooltip>
  </Bar>
</Chart>
```

#### ChartPopover

```jsx
<Chart data={data}>
  <Bar>
    <ChartPopover>
      {(datum, close) => (
        <Content>
          <Text>Average: {datum.average}</Text>
          <ActionButton onPress={close}>Close</ActionButton>
        </Content>
      )}
    </ChartPopover>
  </Bar>
</Chart>
```

